title: Worst Date Wednesday: We Watched Old Family Videos
description: Becca emails us to tell us the story of how she went out with a guy from one of her college houses and right off the bat she gets to his place and realizes he lives at home with his parents.  They were supposed to go ice skating but then he surprises her with no ice skating for her because he was set to play a hockey game and had her come watch.  It only gets worse from there...
